	   <tr><td colspan=2>These sandals are nicer than the newbie monk sandals in Freeport (AC 4 STA+2 AGI+1), as are the bracers. An intrepid monk might want to mix and match items from Qeynos and Freeport to get the best stats as well as for balance, as the FP armor focuses on AGI, while the Qeynos armor seems to emphasize DEX.&nbsp;&nbsp;Have to go both places to do headband and sash quests anyway.<br><br>Just remember to bring woven spider silks from FP, as they are much harder to obtain in WK.  <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Jul  3 20:22:46 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
